    function automatic int reduction_tree_STAGES(int GROUP_SIZE, int DATA_WIDTH);
        if(DATA_WIDTH == 1) return 1;
        return clog_base(GROUP_SIZE, DATA_WIDTH);
    endfunction
"
- correct arguments passed in  
- GROUP_SIZE is the base factor reduction that we are reducing DATA_WIDTH by
- but, we also have a guard, since STAGES cannot be 0 (must be at least 1)
